# 🎯 **What each component does (IMPORTANT)**

| Component  | Role                |
| ---------- | ------------------- |
| Flask API  | Exposes ML model    |
| Docker     | Packages app        |
| Deployment | Runs container      |
| Pod        | Running instance    |
| Service    | Makes it accessible |

