# 🔥 **Common Errors (and fixes)**

### ❌ ImagePullBackOff

✔ Run:

```bash
eval $(minikube docker-env)
docker build -t ml-service .
```

---

### ❌ connection refused

✔ Run:

```bash
minikube start
```

---

### ❌ requirements.txt missing

✔ Ensure file exists in same folder

